title: [Western Waterway]
description: A lone cormorant cries out as it flies towards the northeast beach, its shadow rippling across the water.  A brilliant orange beak sticks out in strong contrast against the pale blue sky.  The faint sound of hammering echoes out across the water.
A lone cormorant cries out from the northeast beach as it settles in for the night.  The moons above create shadows across the water.
